    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius
                        millesimo centesimo quadragesimo quinto, pridie (…), indictione ottava.
                        Manifestus sum ego <persName key="#Priests #Prevosts"><name ref="Albertus"
                                >Albertus</name></persName>, divina gratia <rs key="#Priests"
                            >presbiter</rs> et <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3205" key="#Churches #Monasteries"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterii</rs> sancti Giorgi</orgName> siti <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches">in civitate Luc.</placeName>, quod
                        consensu et consilio cum fratrum suprascripti monasterii, pro utilitate
                        eiusdem ecclesie et monasterio, vendo et trado tibi <persName><name
                                ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>, rectori <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Churches #Hospitals"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs>
                            sancti Gilii de loco <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Churches #Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName></orgName>, ad opus
                        eiusdem hospitalis, idest unam petiam de terra que est campus pertinente
                        suprascripte ecclesie monasterii sancti Georgi, que esse videtur in loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/319">Cappiano</placeName>, ubi dicitur
                            <placeName ref="#places/3228">Ultrario</placeName>. Que tenet unum caput
                        in terra <persName><name ref="Andreas">Andree</name></persName> et aliud
                        caput in terra suprascripti Sancti Georgi quam tenet <persName><name
                                ref="Rainuccius">Ranuccius</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Bocalieri">Bocalieri</name></persName>. Latus unum in terra
                        suprascripti sancti Georgi, quam tenet <persName><name ref="Berno"
                                >Bernuccus</name></persName>, et aliud latus in terra suprascripti
                        sancti Georgi. <foreign>Dimensioni</foreign>: modiorum unum et stariorum
                        ***. <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: solidorum sixaginta lucensis monete. (…)
                        Actum <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Monasteries"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Hericus</name>
                            <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs></persName> domni imperatoris
                        post traditam complevi et dedi. Et repromissio ad defendi contra omnes
                        homines ad penam librarum d. CC ottimi argenti (…).</ab>
